Java IO (Streams)
-----------------

Two Types
--------------
	-> Flat file system
	-> data base

Two Types of Strams
	1. Byte Streams
	2. Character streams
	

1. Byte Stream
--------------------
	-> 8 bit character system
		1. InputStream
		2. OutputStream


2. Character streams
--------------------------
	-> b bit character system
	
		1. Reader
		2. Writer
		
		
	
	
	
			